首批患者出院！武昌方舱医院广场舞组织者出舱了。
First batch of patients discharged! Wuchang square cabin hospital square dance organizer out of the cabin.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 赵思维 廖艳 薛莎莎2月11日16时许，武汉武昌方舱医院首批28名新冠肺炎患者康复出院。
Zhao Xinliao Xue Sha Sha February 11, Wuhan Wuchang cabin hospital, the first 28 patients with new crown pneumonia convalescent discharged.
澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）记者现场看到，来自不同街道办和社区的工作人员提前来到等候区，举牌等患者出院，接他们回集中区域隔离14天。
Journalists from the surging news (www.thepper.cn) saw staff from different street offices and communities arrive early in the waiting area, wait for signs to be discharged, and pick them up in the regroupment area for 14 days.
有出院患者称，方舱医院伙食非常好，内部“环境可以”，病人和医护人员还一起唱歌跳舞，放松心情。
Patients discharged from the hospital said that the cabin hospital food is very good, the internal "environment can", patients and medical personnel together singing and dancing, relaxed mood.
也有患者传授康复经验：一要多喝水；二要吃好睡好；三要心态好，要有信心打败病毒。
There are also patients teach rehabilitation experience: one to drink more water; two to eat good sleep; three must be in a good state of mind, have confidence to defeat the virus.
多名患者均表示，感谢医护人员辛苦的照顾和治疗，他们逆行而上、不怕牺牲的精神值得点赞。
Many patients said that thanks to the hard care and treatment of medical staff, they retrograde, not afraid to sacrifice the spirit of praise.
Play澎湃新闻记者 郑朝渊 赵思维 祝文博 编辑 忻燕 视频来源：澎湃新闻责任编辑：周宽玮开辟专门区域，集中隔离14天武汉方舱医院首批出院的新冠肺炎患者共28人，年龄最大的69岁，主要年龄段在60岁左右。
2007-9-25 21: 55 [hide] www.youtheme.cn Zheng Chaoyuan, journalist, editor-in-chief: Zhou Kuan-wei has set up a special area to isolate the first batch of 28 cases of New Crown Pneumonia from Wuhan Fangcao Hospital for 14 days.
女性患者多于男性患者，男女比例约为1：2。
There are more female patients than male patients, and the ratio is about 1: 2.
首批新冠肺炎患者的出院要求，按照国家卫健委发布的《新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎诊疗方案”（试行第五版）》标准，同时达到4个标准，即体温恢复正常3天以上、呼吸道症状明显好转、肺部影像学显示炎症明显吸收、连续两次呼吸道病原核酸检测为阴性（采样时间间隔至少1天）。
The discharge requirements for the first batch of patients with Newly Coronavirus Infection were met according to the standards of the New Coronavirus Infection Diagnosis and Treatment Scheme (Trial 5th Edition) issued by the National Health Commission.
街道办和社区工作人员在现场举牌接出院患者。
Street offices and community workers put up signs at the scene to receive patients discharged from hospitals.
本文图片均为澎湃新闻记者 赵思维 图记者看到，为庆祝这批患者康复出院，现场竖起了“出舱了！热烈祝贺武昌方舱医院病友康复出舱”的标牌。
Zhao Yintu, a journalist who worked as a journalist, saw the sign "Out of the cabin! Congratulations to the sick man of Wuchang Fang Hospital on his recovery."
来自不同街道办和社区的工作人员提前来到现场，举牌等候康复出院的患者“回家”。
Staff from different street offices and communities arrived early to "go home" with signs waiting to be discharged from the hospital.
街道办和社区工作人员接出院患者回集中隔离点。
Street offices and community workers take discharged patients back to the central isolation point.
武汉市武昌区杨园街道办的曹庭满是来接患者的人员之一。
Wuhan Wuchang District Yangyuan Road Cao Tingman is one of the people who came to receive patients.
他介绍，街道办已经开辟好专门区域，供康复的患者集中隔离观察14天，街道办提供生活必需品，隔离区域也有医护人员照看。
He said the neighborhood office had set up special areas for 14 days of intensive quarantine for recovering patients, with street offices providing daily necessities and isolated areas being looked after by medical staff.
此外，隔离区域还设置了运动设施，如：乒乓球台等。
In addition, sports facilities such as ping-pong tables have been set up in the isolated areas.
李鑫手持“出院证明”向记者竖起大拇指。
Li Xin held a "discharge certificate" to the reporter thumbs up.
“伙食非常好，组织唱歌跳舞”刚出院的李鑫（化名）手持“出院证明”，高兴地向记者竖起大拇指。
"Food is very good, organized singing and dancing" just discharged Li Xin (alias) held "discharge certificate", happy to give reporters thumbs up.
“出院证明”上写着，他今年56岁，于2月6日住进武昌方舱医院。
The discharge certificate said he was 56 years old and had been admitted to Wuchang Fang Hospital on February 6.
经治疗、专家组会诊确认，符合新冠肺炎患者出院标准，准予出院。
After treatment, expert group consultation confirmed that the discharge standards of patients with Newcomost pneumonia, permission to leave the hospital.
出院后，居家隔离14天，不适随诊。
After discharge from the hospital, the home was isolated for 14 days.
李鑫称，他非常感谢医护人员的无私奉献，他们逆行而上、不怕牺牲的精神值得点赞。
Li said he was grateful for the selfless dedication of medical staff, who deserve praise for their spirit of being retrograde and unafraid of sacrifice.
有康复患者介绍，方舱医院伙食非常好，内部“环境可以”，配套设施仍需继续改善，“不能洗澡是最大遗憾”。
There are rehabilitation patients, the cabin hospital food is very good, the internal "environment can", supporting facilities still need to continue to improve, "can not bathe is the greatest regret."
此外，病人和医护人员还一起唱歌、跳舞，放松心情。
In addition, patients and medical personnel together singing, dancing, relaxed mood.
一位患者的“出院证明”。
One patient's "discharge certificate."
今年37岁的张灵（化名）于2月6日在武昌方舱医院住院，11日出院。
Zhang Ling (not his real name), 37, was hospitalized in Wuchang Fang Hospital on February 6 and discharged on February 11.
她介绍，她是方舱医院跳广场舞的组织者，她和病人们沟通、协调，约定好时间后，组织大家一起学习舞蹈。
She said she was the organizer of the square dance at Fang Cao Hospital. She talked with patients, coordinated and arranged a time to learn dance together.
有时，医护人员也会和病人一起学着跳。
Sometimes the paramedics learn to dance with the patient.
非饭点时，跳舞人数有数十人。
There were dozens of dancers on the non-dinner hour.
张灵身体恢复得不错，她也乐于把自己的康复经验分享给别人。
Zhang Ling has recovered well and she is happy to share her healing experiences with others.
“第一要多喝水；第二要吃好睡好，多吃含高蛋白的食物，包括鸡蛋、肉类、虾等；第三要心态好，身体在和病毒战争，要有信心打败它。
"Drink plenty of water first. Second, eat well and eat foods high in protein, including eggs, meat and shrimp.
”张灵说道，“我在外面等大家出来”。
"I'll wait outside for everyone to come out," Zhang said.
还有患者告诉记者：“出院了，我想把身体养得棒棒的，然后去帮助别人！”面对镜头，她鼓励大家：“病友们加油！一切都会好起来的，医务工作者太好了，感谢他们，武汉加油！”武昌方舱医院康复出院的患者合影“医护人员都是战士”也有出院的患者表示，在方舱医院感受到了医护人员的伟大，“虽然没有拿枪，但他们都是战士”。
Another patient told reporters: "I was discharged, I want to raise the body of a baseball bat, and then to help others!" Facing the camera, she encouraged everyone: "Medical workers cheer up, thank them, Wuhan!" Wuchang Square Hospital convalescent patients released from the hospital "all soldiers," said hospital discharged from the hospital felt the great medical staff, "although not gun, they are all fighters.
得知自己核酸检测转阴后，她非常激动，“我能痊愈，真的很感谢医护人员，感谢方舱医院，他们在医疗和生活上都给了我们很大帮助。
When she learned that her nucleic acid test had turned cloudy, she was very excited. "I can get well. I really appreciate the paramedics.
护士们把一日三餐送到我们面前，我们有什么问题，她们都会尽量解决。
The nurses bring us three meals a day and try to solve any problems we have.
”一位约50多岁的康复患者抑制不住出院的激动心情告诉记者，在来方舱医院前，她在医院住院部治疗，“（身体）一天比一天好了，就这么简单”。
A convalescent man in his 50s could not contain her excitement at being discharged from the hospital and told reporters that she was being treated in the hospital's inpatient department in front of Lai Fang Hospital.
约2月6日上午，她转到方舱医院。
On the morning of about 6 February, she was transferred to the cabin hospital.
她称，现在身体很好，最想感谢的是医护人员。
She said she was in good health and wanted to thank the paramedics the most.
46岁的鲁女士在2月6日住进武昌方舱医院，也是首批出院患者中的一员。
Ms. Lu, 46, was one of the first patients to leave hospital in Wuchang on February 6.
鲁女士称，她曾见过一位医护人员身体很虚弱，但仍坚持照顾病人，“这让我非常感动，特别要感谢他们，（如果）没有他们，我不会恢复得这么好。
Ms Lu said she had seen a paramedic who was frail but still insisted on taking care of the patient. "It moved me, especially to thank them, and I wouldn't have recovered so well without them.
”住院期间，鲁女士很心疼医护人员，“一站就是一晚上，不喝水，也不上厕所、也不吃东西，我心里很难受，这让我很感动。
During her stay in the hospital, Ms. Lu was very upset with the medical staff. "One stop was a night without drinking water, going to the toilet or eating.
所以我要早点（康复）出院，为他们减轻些负担。
So I'm going to get out of the hospital early and lighten their burden.
”“出院后最想做什么？”“回家洗个澡。
"What do I want to do after I leave the hospital?" "Go home and have a bath.
”鲁女士笑着说道。
"said Mrs Roux, smiling.
（实习生孟津津、胡友美、夏梦洁、李宁馨、李娴对本文亦有贡献）本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
(Intern Mengjin, Hu Youmei, Xia Mengjie, Li Ning Xin, Li Xian also contributed to this article) This edition editor Chang Chen recommends reading.
